name: GTA: SA
description:
Process : I loaded up GTA: San Andreas on my PS2, sent it through a video mixer to my TV. I then recorded it via an old style camcorder which sent it to my OBS on my laptop. I then recorded it and did some slight editing to make it right.

Reason : This work is part of a CHARITY to help victims of the natural disaster from Mount Semeru eruption, every sale in the first market will be 100% donated to the victims, through sewon NFT #tezos4semeru
